  <brief_title>Study About the Effect of Doxycycline and Acetylcystein in the Treatment of CD-associated Fistulae</brief_title>
  <official_title>FIST-MC-09 Study About the Effect of Doxycycline and Acetylcystein in the Treatment of CD-associated Fistulae</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Gerhard Rogler</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of Zurich</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will study whether local instillation of Doxycycline and Acetylcystein
      results in fistula closure in CD patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
